column5: Great shots of Cheminis Solo. I remember seeing it many moons ago when I was up fishing at a buddies cabin on Muldrew Lake just outside of V-town.  Thanks for sharing.  Nemo
Just curious but do you mean Mulven lake?
Thanks Mike for the afternoon fish porn!  What beautiful scenery and great fishing to boot!  I've got to get on your fishing list! Your reports are killing me.  Stan
Sorry Solo, yes Mulven, got confused with the other Lake in a previous post.
Awesome report Mike, thanks.  Love reading about and seeing your adventures - very beautiful place your uncle has there.

WOW...awesome fishing trip/report mike !!!!   great scenery,and fishing spots,man all that water & rapids,it must have been hard to keep moving,and to not want to just stop and keep fishing,so much water so little time !!! thanks for sharing,im looking forward to your part #2 of your fishing trip!!!...cheers
Thanx Mike..  I feel good all over..  Freaking incredible!!  HD
Thanks Rene. I'm pretty sure you know exactly where I was fishing as well  .
